<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 12:28:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>萨巴伦卡目标排名第一，为精彩赛季画上完美句号</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-targets-top-ranking-cap-off-superb-season-2024-09-24/</link><description>世界排名第二的阿琳娜·萨巴连卡(Aryna Sabalenka)将在中国公开赛赢得美国公开赛胜利后首次重返赛场，白俄罗斯选手周二表示，她的目标是在本赛季最后几周重新夺回最高排名。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-targets-top-ranking-cap-off-superb-season-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着亚洲海底竞争的加剧，新加坡委托建造两艘新潜艇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-commissions-two-new-submarines-asias-undersea-rivalry-grows-2024-09-24/</link><description>新加坡周二委托建造两艘新型先进潜艇，其海军表示，这艘潜艇旨在保护海上交通线，专家表示，这艘潜艇将在这个小城国家的水域之外航行，以监视该地区的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-commissions-two-new-submarines-asias-undersea-rivalry-grows-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>由于市场等待降息线索，期货走低；中国的刺激措施提振了矿商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-rise-soft-landing-optimism-china-stimulus-2024-09-24/</link><description>周二，美国股指期货在震荡交易中保持沉默，因投资者寻找有关美联储下一步可能采取的政策举措的线索，而在中国推出丰厚的刺激计划后，矿业股受到提振。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-rise-soft-landing-optimism-china-stimulus-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：中国经济放缓，欧洲打喷嚏，新高在召唤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>美联储降息对面临中国竞争的美国工厂的缓解作用有限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-rate-cut-offers-limited-relief-us-factories-facing-china-competition-2024-09-24/</link><description>美国生产商正面临低利率无法缓解的逆风。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:05:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-rate-cut-offers-limited-relief-us-factories-facing-china-competition-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾 8 月出口订单超出预期，人工智能需求强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-august-export-orders-beat-forecasts-solid-demand-ai-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于人工智能（AI）应用芯片的需求持续攀升，台湾 8 月份的出口订单超出预期，政府预计这一强劲势头将延续到今年剩余时间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-august-export-orders-beat-forecasts-solid-demand-ai-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国调查美国PVH公司涉嫌抵制新疆产品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-probes-us-firm-pvh-over-suspected-boycotting-xinjiang-products-2024-09-24/</link><description>商务部周二表示，中国将对 Calvin Klein 和 Tommy Hilfiger 的母公司 PVH 涉嫌违反涉疆产品市场交易原则进行调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:31:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-probes-us-firm-pvh-over-suspected-boycotting-xinjiang-products-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激措施推动欧洲股市上涨；奢侈品股大放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-jump-china-stimulus-luxury-stocks-shine-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于中国全面的刺激措施提振了奢侈品公司和矿业公司的股票，欧洲股市周二上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:45:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-jump-china-stimulus-luxury-stocks-shine-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激措施提振矿业和奢侈品股，伦敦股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-shares-jump-china-stimulus-lifts-mining-luxury-stocks-2024-09-24/</link><description>英国股市周二跟随全球涨幅上涨，因市场对中国新的刺激措施表示欢迎，这些措施提振了矿业公司和专注于奢侈品的零售商的股价。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-shares-jump-china-stimulus-lifts-mining-luxury-stocks-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国零跑汽车和Stellantis在欧洲开放廉价电动汽车订单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-stellantis-open-orders-europe-budget-evs-2024-09-24/</link><description>周二，中国零跑汽车及其合作伙伴 Stellantis 表示，该公司将开始在欧洲接受一款城市轿车和一款 SUV 的订单，以扩大其在该地区的廉价电动汽车 (EV) 产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-stellantis-open-orders-europe-budget-evs-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称中国是俄罗斯武器外国技术的关键途径</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-china-is-key-route-foreign-tech-russian-weapons-2024-09-24/</link><description>乌克兰总统顾问弗拉迪斯拉夫·弗拉休克周二对记者表示，在乌克兰战场上发现的俄罗斯武器中大约60%的外国零部件来自中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:25:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-china-is-key-route-foreign-tech-russian-weapons-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>卢比停止连涨，远期保费维持在 18 个月高位附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-halts-winning-streak-forward-premiums-hold-near-18-month-high-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于进口商通常以美元付款，印度卢比的涨势将于周二停止，而在美联储官员发表鸽派言论后，远期升水保持在数月高位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-halts-winning-streak-forward-premiums-hold-near-18-month-high-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>受伤的拉杜卡努成为最新退出中国公开赛的大牌球员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-raducanu-latest-big-name-pull-out-china-open-2024-09-24/</link><description>Elena Rybakina、Iga Swiatek 和 Ons Jabeur 也将缺席北京的比赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-raducanu-latest-big-name-pull-out-china-open-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲高级官员称摩根大通看好印度和日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jpmorgan-bullish-india-japan-top-asia-official-says-2024-09-24/</link><description>美国最大银行摩根大通一位高级官员表示，看好亚洲的印度和日本，但也热衷于将资源配置到受益于“中国加一”战略的东南亚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:48:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jpmorgan-bullish-india-japan-top-asia-official-says-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出大范围降息和其他刺激措施以刺激疲软的经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rolls-out-broad-rate-cuts-other-stimulus-spur-weak-economy-2024-09-24/</link><description>中国周二宣布了一系列广泛的刺激措施，以支持步履蹒跚的经济、稳定房地产业并恢复市场信心。消息公布后，股票和债券大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rolls-out-broad-rate-cuts-other-stimulus-spur-weak-economy-2024-09-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>